                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">through an interpreter.</hi>) I was in a public-house, and two or three men were ill-using me, and going to beat me—I came out to call the watchman—I and my shipmate stood together talking—the prisoner came by and took my handkerchief out of my pocket—I directly took hold of his hand, and gave him in charge, and found the handkerchief in his hand.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350921-name-316" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350921-name-316" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
